
### Results that are exactly 0.95

```{r, results='asis'}
# check results at 0.95
check95 = filter(results, 
               digits == 2,
               auc == 0.95) %>%
  sample_n(n_check)
for (k in 1:n_check){
  cat('* ', start, check95$pmid[k], '\n', sep='')
}  
cat('[link](',check95$pmid[k],')', sep='')
```
